>\n大d睇既係悲劇<br />\n到咁上下年紀睇係哲理<br />\n<br />\n淨係咁一雞三味既港產電影都無乜邊套做到喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T04:29:48.000Z","msg":"好認同～特別係最尾城樓劍客一幕，臨尾一句：&quot;成隻狗咁&quot;。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbetween<br />\n從前現在過去再不來<br />\n紅紅落葉長埋塵土內<br />\n開始終結總是沒變改<br />\n天邊的你飄泊白雲外<br />\n<br />\n＊苦海翻起愛恨　在世間難逃避命運<br />\n相親竟不可接近<br />\n<br />\n或我應該相信是緣份<br />\n<br />\n情人別後永遠再不來(消散的情緣)<br />\n無言獨坐放眼塵世外(愿來日再續)<br />\n鮮花雖會凋謝(只愿)<br />\n但會再開(為你)<br />\n一生所愛隱約(守候)<br />\n在白雲外(期待)<br />\n<br />\n重唱　＊,＊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5efcd27be35e8eb14390808877566981a67ac7cb","tid":777492,"uid":37537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T04:34:20.000Z","msg":"個個位都有存在主義/荒誕<br />\n對我來講一定係神作"},{"pid":"89acc597ee71a1f8933b0342393f3be7ba2e16d9","tid":777492,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T04:37:17.000Z","msg":"吹大咗啦"},{"pid":"40fa2ed176d855a7c67549eb4b6c1550c00bc4a2","tid":777492,"uid":37537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5efcd27be35e8eb14390808877566981a67ac7cb","tid":777492,"uid":37537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T04:34:20.000Z","msg":"個個位都有存在主義/荒誕<br />\n對我來講一定係神作"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T04:38:40.000Z","msg":"當然佛家解讀又得"},{"pid":"54904d1ebce8ac498a8729fd0086b7fc837462b6","tid":777492,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T04:39:08.000Z","msg":"口味既野<br />\n大家唔同咪算囉<br />\n一定要質疑??"},{"pid":"a77315ccc9d9d2b738942b1928f3eb716a3fcd49","tid":777492,"uid":54957,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T04:40:59.000Z","msg":"早幾日Netflix有 即刻睇多次 好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"180ae0fd5e89bdf2c87fcc1c848e3d6c53663257","tid":777492,"uid":37537,"like":0